<h1 id="title">XML Query Working Group Charter</h1>

<p class="mission">The <strong>mission</strong> of the <a
href="http://www.w3.org/XML/Query/">XML Query Working Group</a>, part of the
<a href="http://www.w3.org/XML/">Extensible Markup Language (XML)
Activity</a>, is to provide flexible query facilities to extract data from
XML and virtual documents, such as contents of databases or other persistent
storage that are viewed as XML via a mapping mechanism, on the Web.</p>

<div class="noprint">
<p class="join"><a href="http://www.w3.org/2004/01/pp-impl/18797/join">Join
the XML Query Working Group</a>.</p>
</div>

